00:00:26.520 --> 00:00:34.680
use Generative AI as an R programmer. Now initially, this all started because I

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:41.000
was a bit fearful of Generative AI. I was really afraid that large language

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.840
models were going to take my job, or worse, take over the world, and so I

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:49.439
wanted to learn more about how these models worked and I wanted to understand

00:00:49.439 --> 00:00:55.279
