00:01:18.879 --> 00:01:23.959
about data science more broadly. I wanted to talk about it with anyone who would

00:01:23.959 --> 00:01:28.839
let me, and whenever one of my friends or someone online would be skeptical

00:01:28.839 --> 00:01:33.919
about how useful the technology actually is, I was the one jumping into the

00:01:33.919 --> 00:01:38.919
conversation and proclaiming that this was the next big world-changing thing.

00:01:38.919 --> 00:01:48.199
And in some ways, I was definitely right. There's no denying that Generative AI has

00:01:48.199 --> 00:01:55.959
