edit the video itself. So if I've got this paragraph highlighted here and then

00:38:47.360 --> 00:38:51.760
I delete that paragraph it's going to automatically trim the video to the

00:38:51.760 --> 00:38:57.919
correct locations. With the click of a button you can do things like remove

00:38:57.919 --> 00:39:02.560
awkward silences and filler words which is great if you're someone who's guilty

00:39:02.560 --> 00:39:10.639
of saying um way too much. Descript also has AI speech generation capabilities

00:39:10.639 --> 00:39:16.919
and you can make a clone of your own voice in as little as 60 seconds. So if

00:39:16.919 --> 00:39:19.959
you don't like the way that a word sounded when you originally recorded it

