you can use your voice clone to regenerate the content. And if you don't

00:39:26.679 --> 00:39:30.479
like the wording that you used and you want to change that up altogether then

00:39:30.479 --> 00:39:35.080
you can use the overdub feature to replace it without needing to re-record

00:39:35.080 --> 00:39:42.040
the clip. Descript also has a lot of other really cool AI power features as

